既野"},{"pid":"be416b764c45cad8979d9f0cb118d0783f3ef5c1","tid":302452,"uid":25319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>google過好多文都睇唔明<br />\n到底promise同resolver係咩黎同有咩用<br />\n同埋咩同步異步又係咩黎<br />\n有冇人可以簡單講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nNodeJS?<br />\npromise大概係用黎解決callback hell同async問題， 果時我用都冇話好深入了解， 但就咁估promise同「袋住先」差唔多， 之後好似仲有個.then既野</blockquote><br />\nwaterfall?"},{"pid":"4fd5999cd4e065b4e18eae2127779ccab371cb21","tid":302452,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T14:46:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>google過好多文都睇唔明<br />\n到底promise同resolver係咩黎同有咩用<br />\n同埋咩同步異步又係咩黎<br />\n有冇人可以簡單講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nNodeJS?<br />\npromise大概係用黎解決callback hell同async問題， 果時我用都冇話好深入了解， 但就咁估promise同「袋住先」差唔多， 之後好似仲有個.then既野</blockquote><br />\nthen係return promise，唔係袋住先，同埋可以用.all啲promises"},{"pid":"95f831a60b2de8f327d008963bad788ab85892c1","tid":302452,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T15:11:59.000Z","msg":"async await<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e3ff9e77dd272b738d4a4640523fb9df9dffe6","tid":302452,"uid":101593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T15:44:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>async await<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nasync await係咪可以完成取代promise"},{"pid":"e57f701e3e3d2dff82a9efab59963c6318a75d8c","tid":302452,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T16:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>async await<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nasync await係咪可以完成取代promise</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都冇話代唔代替到嘅, 跟番呢篇(<a href=\"https://appendto.com/2017/06/asyncawait-come-use\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappendto.com%2F2017%2F06%2Fasyncawait-come-use&d=wYcR8OGjEg2myXYcDAheuTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=33c33e1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://appendto.com/2017/06/asyncawait-come-use</a>/)嘢話齋, async/await會包裝得靚仔啲, 易main啲; 但你如果唔嫌棄嗰啲special syntax for error handling, 又不屑用番傳統try...catch嘅話, 咪用番promise囉! Anyway, 有新嘢唔用用舊嘢, 有點兒罪大惡極囉!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5159acdb8acd2d26497c62b632facc2aff93d8","tid":302452,"uid":79869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T17:54:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>async await<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nasync await係咪可以完成取代promise</blockquote><br />\n唔得，async都係base on Promise"},{"pid":"504b4a7b9a0cfc9ace7a902b7592c66c9b35f49c","tid":302452,"uid":79869,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T17:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>async await<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nasync await係咪可以完成取代promise</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都冇話代唔代替到嘅, 跟番呢篇(<a href=\"https://appendto.com/2017/06/asyncawait-come-use\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappendto.com%2F2017%2F06%2Fasyncawait-come-use&d=wYcR8OGjEg2myXYcDAheuTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=33c33e1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://appendto.com/2017/06/asyncawait-come-use</a>/)嘢話齋, async/await會包裝得靚仔啲, 易main啲; 但你如果唔嫌棄嗰啲special syntax for error handling, 又不屑用番傳統try...catch嘅話, 咪用番promise囉! Anyway, 有新嘢唔用用舊嘢, 有點兒罪大惡極囉!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nES2018 = Typescript"},{"pid":"6973c205a188cb730a2947acd6643ee2d37df445","tid":302452,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T18:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>google過好多文都睇唔明<br />\n到底promise同resolver係咩黎同有咩用<br />\n同埋咩同步異步又係咩黎<br />\n有冇人可以簡單講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n簡單黎講, promise 比你define async procedure , 立刻return 返黎, 行完async procedure 會call callback (resolve, reject ) , 你可以用promise.then define resolve ,reject function"},{"pid":"2cfc88e8cfba0f78bf538172fb93b101dea30ce4","tid":302452,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T18:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>async await<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nasync await係咪可以完成取代promise</blockquote><br />\n唔得，async都係base on Promise</blockquote><br />\n係, under the hood, async/await其實都係promise黎; 係包裝得更靚仔既promise, 同時俾你用番try...catch黎handle番D errors.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8ef93f0610c7b8ecc3c85315cdd6b335e64314","tid":302452,"uid":101593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T18:49:31.000Z","msg":"promise作用就係限死左一定要完成A, 先可以執行B?<br />\n我有冇理解錯?"},{"pid":"5a1344df3a709202830173d0d2a4485d9c324cb1","tid":302452,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T19:36:02.000Z","msg":"叫async 但係實際做緊嘅野係sync<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec2659a8b790d41c3618f6db78ee98dec378470","tid":302452,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T22:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>promise作用就係限死左一定要完成A, 先可以執行B?<br />\n我有冇理解錯?</blockquote><br />\n你講嘅係Serial, 但係亦可以Parallel<br />\nPromise最大作用係令啲Code順眼好多<br />\n即係所謂嘅Callback hell, 好似if-else嗰隻波動拳咁<br />\n大幅提升閱讀性，同埋可以集中喺一個地方Handle error<br />\n&lt;pre&gt;<br />\nif (err) {<br />\n  callback(err);<br />\n} else {<br />\n  anotherAsync(function (err, result) {<br />\n    if (err) {<br />\n      callback(err);<br />\n    } else {<br />\n      ... <br />\n    }<br />\n  });<br />\n}<br />\n&lt;/pre&gt;<br />\n變成<br />\n&lt;pre&gt;<br />\npromise.then(...).then(...).catch(function (err) {<br />\n  handleError(err);<br />\n});<br />\n&lt;/pre&gt;<br />\nES7嘅 async/await寫法就係<br />\n&lt;pre&gt;<br />\nasync function doSomething () {<br />\n  try {<br />\n    let result = await myAsyncFunction();<br />\n    let finalResult = await myAnotherAsyncFunction(result);<br />\n    return finalResult;<br />\n  } catch (err) {<br />\n    handleError(err);<br />\n  }<br />\n}<br />\nlet finalResult = doSomething();<br />\n&lt;/pre&gt;<br />\n呢個寫法甚至可以當所有async係sync咁用return<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ef500b9f8b4041e42f55c38f09ec51ea7667c8","tid":302452,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:48:08.000Z","msg":"promise, resolver 點 handle stream??"},{"pid":"d06d6eb0b2509293bd7eda1c31194b70d9b2ef58","tid":302452,"uid":79869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>promise, resolver 點 handle stream??</blockquote><br />\n唔handle😜<br />\n用RxJS la"},{"pid":"bfe269b9f15f56dc9628d7e9f884e79423fa9f0b","tid":302452,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>promise, resolver 點 handle stream??</blockquote><br />\n唔handle😜<br />\n用RxJS la</blockquote><br />\n所以感覺 promise 同 async await 都係半完成品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9387eee83db54b8990cc0f592c51973dc90212be","tid":302452,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>promise, resolver 點 handle stream??</blockquote><br />\n唔handle😜<br />\n用RxJS la</blockquote><br />\n所以感覺 promise 同 async await 都係半完成品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果完成咗跟手又出新嘢代替, 之前嘅嘢即刻obsolete埋, 咪仲sad!<br />\n(等佢慢慢進化下咪幾好! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"e8739e95d11fb16ee2b79bf464e49c2799189e09","tid":302452,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:47:25.000Z","msg":"搭單問下<br />\nExtJS係咩黎"},{"pid":"68aee3d37f73eaf8e88e845d8ae2e6a3e2991e3a","tid":302452,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問下<br />\nExtJS係咩黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇乜人用, 見錢開眼, 多bugs到爆嘅UI framework, 你唔係想用呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(盛惠US$4,340/5-licenses, 至少要買5個喎!)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.slant.co/versus/35/10513/~extjs_vs_react\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.slant.co%2Fversus%2F35%2F10513%2F~extjs_vs_react&d=wYcR8OGjEg2myXYcDAheuTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f4dde447\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.slant.co/versus/35/10513/~extjs_vs_react</a>"},{"pid":"4f68459f58c2b3e959266ecf0212377f75a63d71","tid":302452,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭單問下<br />\nExtJS係咩黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇乜人用, 見錢開眼, 多bugs到爆嘅UI framework, 你唔係想用呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(盛惠US$4,340/5-licenses, 至少要買5個喎!)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.slant.co/versus/35/10513/~extjs_vs_react\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.slant.co%2Fversus%2F35%2F10513%2F~extjs_vs_react&d=wYcR8OGjEg2myXYcDAheuTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f4dde447\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.slant.co/versus/35/10513/~extjs_vs_react</a></blockquote><br />\n唔係想用。<br />\n今日行過黃金， 書鋪有好幾本講extJS, 我未見過所以問下。<br />\n<br />\n仲見到&lt;&lt;駭客的自白&gt;&gt;。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}